                </p>
              </li>

              <li permid="NQb">
                <p permid="aOn">
                  <m> \lim_{b \to \infty} \int_1^b \frac{1}{x^{3/2}} dx = \lim_{b \to \infty} \left( 2 - \frac{2}{\sqrt{b}} \right) = 2</m>
                </p>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </p>
        </li>

        <li permid="aet">
          <p permid="GVw">
            Both graphs have a vertical asymptote at <m>x = 0</m> and for both graphs,
            the <m>x</m>-axis is a horizontal asymptote.
            However, the graph of
